basic.Source: Synthetic construct(derived from the Membrane-Proximal Ectodomain of Feline Immunodeficiency Virus)
basic.Target Organism: [Ref.12610147]FIV-M2(Feline immunodeficiency virus M2):inhibition of virus replication in MBM cells(IC50=0.15 ± 0.01 µg/ml);FIV-GL8(Feline immunodeficiency virus GL8):inhibition of virus replication in MBM cells(IC50=0.64± 0.08 µg/ml);FIV-Pet(Feline immunodeficiency virus Pet):inhibition of virus replication in MBM cells(IC50=0.13 ± 0.04 µg/ml).
